data.description: Welcome to this charming brick home nestled in the serene neighborhood of Two Creeks. This property boasts a blend of original character & potential for modernization, making it a perfect canvas for your dream home. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the timeless beauty of original hardwood floors that grace the main floor. The main level offers a spacious kitchen ready for your creative touch, providing an excellent opportunity to customize & create the culinary space you've always desired. The main floor also features a generously sized dining room, perfect for hosting gatherings. Adjacent to the dining room is a cozy living room, ideal for relaxation & entertainment. Two bedrooms on this level provide convenience & accessibility, along with a full bathroom featuring a walk-in bathtub. Upstairs, you'll discover two additional bedrooms, one with custom built-ins, & each offering unique potential and versatility. A full bathroom on this floor provides convenience for family & guests. Venturing to the basement, you'll find an additional non-conforming bedroom. The basement also houses the laundry room & a spacious living area. While this house presents an opportunity for updates & personalization, the outdoor space is a true gem. The stamped patio is perfect for entertaining, whether you're hosting BBQs, or simply enjoying the tranquility of your backyard. A greenhouse & shed provide options for gardening enthusiasts & extra storage, allowing you to nurture your green thumb. For added convenience, this property includes a 2-car attached, side-loading garage. The light rail is moments away. In close proximity to Wadsworth Blvd, shopping, & dining. With your vision and personal touches, this house can become the perfect place to call home. Don't miss the chance to make it your own & unlock its full potential! This property is zoned M-R-U. See supplements for specifics on adding an ADU or use of group home.
